  "id": "6a0414fa45fdf5278075a80f",
  "title": "サム・アルトマンが紙によるメモを激推ししている",
  "created": 1778652426,
  "updated": 1778672473,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a0414fa45fdf5278075a80f",
      "text": "サム・アルトマンが紙によるメモを激推ししている",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652426,
      "updated": 1778652426
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0418e40000000000172548",
      "text": "[サム・アルトマン]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778653413,
      "updated": 1778653420
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0418ec0000000000172549",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778653420,
      "updated": 1778653420
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04150a0000000000244a93",
      "text": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DAZTC7UpkD7 ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652426,
      "updated": 1778672467
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04156e0000000000244a98",
      "text": " > /* OpenAI's CEO only uses 2 types of pens to take notes */",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652526,
      "updated": 1778656066
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0415940000000000244a99",
      "text": " > I'm a huge ****",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652564,
      "updated": 1778656066
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0415a80000000000244a9a",
      "text": "  I'm a huge /uh-n-t-ey-k-n/",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652584,
      "updated": 1778656066
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0415d80000000000244a9b",
      "text": "  何とおっしゃっているのか聞き取れなかった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652632,
      "updated": 1778656554
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0424e000000000004479df",
      "text": " > There is always like fancy note ?pass? in the world.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656480,
      "updated": 1778656536
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04252400000000004479e0",
      "text": "  何とおっしゃっているのか聞き取れなかった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656548,
      "updated": 1778656552
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04253200000000004479e2",
      "text": " > Yet you don't want those.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656563,
      "updated": 1778656580
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04254400000000004479e3",
      "text": "  こう言ってる？",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656580,
      "updated": 1778656584
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0420af0000000000eeb46c",
      "text": " >You definitely want a spiral notebook because one thing that's important is you can rip pages out (more) frequently. ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778655408,
      "updated": 1778656590
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0421eb0000000000eeb474",
      "text": " > And you also want it to lie like a fly and open the table.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778655723,
      "updated": 1778656066
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0421f30000000000eeb475",
      "text": " > And if you like open pages, you want them to like, you know, like, be able to lay like this, whatever.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778655731,
      "updated": 1778656610
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0422940000000000eeb478",
      "text": "  > [https://gyazo.com/191d116cb976e16dbdff7726ecca8e44]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778655892,
      "updated": 1778656066
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0422950000000000eeb479",
      "text": " > You definitely wanna be /???/ rip pages out. I'm big believer of, I take a bunch of notes and then I clearly rip them out so I can look at multiple pages at the same time.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778655893,
      "updated": 1778656634
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0416140000000000244a9c",
      "text": " > And I can crumple them up and throw them on the floor when I'm done. When our house cleaner comes in and they got out.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652692,
      "updated": 1778656155
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04239b00000000004479d8",
      "text": " > There's just this pile of crumpled papers that I type my notes in or whatever on the floor",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656155,
      "updated": 1778656689
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0425c600000000004479e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656711,
      "updated": 1778656711
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04242e00000000004479db",
      "text": " > You definitely want a kind of paper that is good to write on, which is a feel thing but most paper is terrible to write on.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656303,
      "updated": 1778656711
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04247b00000000004479dc",
      "text": " > You want hard, front and back, to the notepad ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656379,
      "updated": 1778656404
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04249300000000004479dd",
      "text": " > and you also want something  that can fit in a pocket",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656404,
      "updated": 1778656414
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0424a300000000004479de",
      "text": " >I was about to say that.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656419,
      "updated": 1778656443
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04150d0000000000244a94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778652429,
      "updated": 1778656718
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0425ce00000000004479e6",
      "text": " > I think Uni-ball Micro 0.5 Pen is the best pen ovaerall.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656718,
      "updated": 1778656748
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0425ec00000000004479e7",
      "text": " > But the Muji 0.36 or 0.37 in dark blue ink is a very nice pen for other reasons.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656749,
      "updated": 1778656802
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04262400000000004479ea",
      "text": " > So those are two I would use.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656804,
      "updated": 1778656813
    },
    {
      "id": "6a04263100000000004479ec",
      "text": " > but I think this kind of notebook and one of thouse to pen is the right answer.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778656817,
      "updated": 1778656846
    },
    {
